tool_description:
https://xlsx-template.kurukona.net/
Template + JSON ➞ XLSX or PDF.
Template base excel file and pdf generator.
You can create xlsx document or pdf file with template and json data.

optional_parameters.name: replaceFonts
optional_parameters.description:
If only the font name is specified, all fonts are converted. 
ex: `{replaceFonts: "Noto Sans CJK JP"} `

A specific target font can be specified in json format. 
ex:  `{replaceFonts: {"Yu Gothic": "Noto Sans CJK JP"} }`
